<div id="c4">
<p>Chicken is healthier mostly because it has less fat - burgers are pretty high in fat, and also in added sugar. But lean red meat can also be healthy in moderation.</p>

<p>To answer Duck, soda without sugar doesn&#8217;t directly lead to diabetes. But my experience is that it reinforces the desire for sweetness in general.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by Eric Gunnerson
