<div id="c5">
<p>&#8220;Dark meat when grilled can lead to potential carcinogens.&#8221; Huh?  Grilling <i>any</i> food leads to carcinogens, so I don&#8217;t know what that statement means. Cooking processes in general introduce far more carcinogens into your diet than pesticides and artificial additives ever will.</p>

<p>BTW: it occurs to me that people who express concern about extending their lives tend not to be at the end of their lives that actually gets extended.</p>

